{"tid":2140144,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"急問!!!求vba 大神解救","createTime":"2020-08-04T19:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T08:19:47.000Z","uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b65b10c68c49b2f6b7608ffdd9b90ab1f83ad583","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T19:19:17.000Z","msg":"事關小弟有份excel table 要交<br />\n<br />\n但係呢 砌formula 都係半桶水<br />\n個table 係咁嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QosCzqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQosCzqP.png&h=f44f84ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nName 同counting 係input data <br />\n不過係Random input 即係 今次A 下次有可能係ABC 唔順次序嘅<br />\n<br />\n而output 係range 係跟據最新A同上一項A嘅counting 計出嚟嘅range<br />\n<br />\n用formula 又多左行出黎 <br />\n<br />\n而我想每次個output 可以自動gen 出嚟<br />\n上過好多網搵都唔似係呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n跪求 各位大大 有冇網站或者相關字推介係講相關嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43eaa4f0f8cd6a2ea26e17dfc91b1c1c1fc1ab6","tid":2140144,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"根據最新A同上個A計<br />\n即係點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6300a52715b7829fb683294c9e464e060f68a0ed","tid":2140144,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"即係<br />\nRandom順序入<br />\nA1<br />\nA2<br />\nB1<br />\nC1<br />\nA3<br />\n然後A3個range就係|A3-A2|?"},{"pid":"a5115576233c00fab503c7b88032b800a5c1d624","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43eaa4f0f8cd6a2ea26e17dfc91b1c1c1fc1ab6","tid":2140144,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"根據最新A同上個A計<br />\n即係點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"即係 <br />\nFor Name A<br />\ncell C3=cell B3-cell B2 (5-1=4)<br />\ncell C9=cell B9-cell B3(8-5=3)<br />\n<br />\nFor Name B<br />\ncell C8=cell B8-cell B4 (8-3=5)<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n即係 我個name 同counting係 input <br />\n例如 我column 12新input<br />\nName A counting 20  <br />\n因為呢4係A第四次出現<br />\n佢個range 會同第三次出現A嘅Counting 相減<br />\n<br />\n唔該師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbb361c1ac9808ecc03e6071e1c52901816e982","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6300a52715b7829fb683294c9e464e060f68a0ed","tid":2140144,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"即係<br />\nRandom順序入<br />\nA1<br />\nA2<br />\nB1<br />\nC1<br />\nA3<br />\n然後A3個range就係|A3-A2|?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"可以咁講<br />\n睇返我依家個表係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbGseGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbGseGC.png&h=3d78346d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA1<br />\nA2<br />\nB1<br />\nA3<br />\nC1<br />\nC2<br />\nB2<br />\nA3<br />\nB3<br />\nC3<br />\n<br />\n而跟著個column 會入嘅會係<br />\nA4或者B4或者C4<br />\n<br />\n我當我入完 B4<br />\n跟著個column 會入嘅會係<br />\nA4或者B5或者C4<br />\n<br />\n唔該大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2957283540861e6a035bd8d6dad6eb1c3029c5bd","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6300a52715b7829fb683294c9e464e060f68a0ed","tid":2140144,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"即係<br />\nRandom順序入<br />\nA1<br />\nA2<br />\nB1<br />\nC1<br />\nA3<br />\n然後A3個range就係|A3-A2|?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"A3個range就係|A3個counting-A2個counting|<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9483a98fd536468713be87d45b2cb6c755495ecc","tid":2140144,"uid":238920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"不如你直接人手打個結果出黎俾人睇啦<br />\n講到1999咁<img src=\"/assets/