"9d60f277adaf9760e11449186d8baa4b651cd050","tid":2140144,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fa3649aec8144f37061d3b0b7d820be280db215","tid":2140144,"uid":183367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"我會用powershell...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"我應該會用Assembly <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3e2a81ac7443f484e12ee7d5edbc113ac26f90","tid":2140144,"uid":138715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"用Private Sub Worksheet_Change(ByVal Target As Range)<br />\ncondition 係 Col A 同B 既input<br />\n之後用countif  個名, =1 就vlookup<br />\n詳細等其他巴打補充?"},{"pid":"e4f51d01ddd015adc0f31b356bc764b7d618269f","tid":2140144,"uid":160122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"同你用FORMULA搞，唔使逗VBA<br />\n<br />\n由C3開始：<br />\n<code>=IFNA($B3-INDEX($B$2:$B2,XMATCH($A3,$A$2:$A2,0,-1)),&quot;-&quot;)</code><br />\n<br />\nINDEX ( <span class=\"blue\">$B$2:$B2</span> , XMATCH ( <span class=\"brown\">$A3</span>, <span class=\"purple\">$A$2:$A2</span> , 0, -1 ) ) )<br />\n呢部分講緊喺 <span class=\"purple\">$A$2:$A2</span> （即係A欄最頂$A$2到嗰行對上最後一格，以第3行嚟講係$A2，再拉落去第4行$A$2都仲係$A$2，$A2就會係$A3）搵<span class=\"brown\">$A3</span>個value喺邊行，對應返<span class=\"blue\">$B$2:$B2</span>（即係$A$2:$A2移去B欄）同一格個value<br />\n<br />\n我工作上成日用INDEX、MATCH嚟搵第一個exact match（即係MATCH function 第三嗰個「0」），但係你個case要搵最後一個value我以為搞唔到，直到發現原來有XMATCH呢樣嘢，最後嗰個「-1」就係叫XMATCH唔由頭掃落去而係由最底掃返上去，所以就做到「搵最後一個出現嘅value」個效果了<br />\n<br />\n$B3 - INDEX(...) 唔解釋，如果 INDEX(...) 出N/A（即係上面啲data未MATCH到嘢），咁個IFNA就幫你整個「-」出嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過呢條式無得套入去C2（又唔係完全唔得嘅，只係邏輯上唔consistant，因為佢對上唔會有data），嗰個位你就自己硬食個「-」入去算嘞"},{"pid":"b731861e2e28a363526d8f213af0f320aa11a106","tid":2140144,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"77deec19bcfe3aa7e5b0b78be22360ac8412e326","tid":2140144,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f51d01ddd015adc0f31b356bc764b7d618269f","tid":2140144,"uid":160122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"同你用FORMULA搞，唔使逗VBA<br />\n<br />\n由C3開始：<br />\n<code>=IFNA($B3-INDEX($B$2:$B2,XMATCH($A3,$A$2:$A2,0,-1)),&quot;-&quot;)</code><br />\n<br />\nINDEX ( <span class=\"blue\">$B$2:$B2</span> , XMATCH ( <span class=\"brown\">$A3</span>, <span class=\"purple\">$A$2:$A2</span> , 0, -1 ) ) )<br />\n呢部分講緊喺 <span class=\"purple\">$A$2:$A2</span> （即係A欄最頂$A$2到嗰行對上最後一格，以第3行嚟講係$A2，再拉落去第4行$A$2都仲係$A$2，$A2就會係$A3）搵<span class=\"brown\">$A3</span>個value喺邊行，對應返<span class=\"blue\">$B$2:$B2</span>（即係$A$2:$A2移去B欄）同一格個value<br />\n<br />\n我工作上成日用INDEX、MATCH嚟搵第一個exact match（即係MATCH function 第三嗰個「0」），但係你個case要搵最後一個value我以為搞唔到，直到發現原來有XMATCH呢樣嘢，最後嗰個「-1」就係叫XMATCH唔由頭掃落去而係由最底掃返上去，所以就做到「搵最後一個出現嘅value」個效果了<br />\n<br />\n$B3 - INDEX(...) 唔解釋，如果 INDEX(...) 出N/A（即係上面啲data未MATCH到嘢），咁個IFNA就幫你整個「-」出嚟<br />\n<br />\n不過呢條式無得套入去C2（又唔係完全唔得嘅，只係邏輯上唔consistant，因為佢對上唔會有data），嗰個位你就自己硬食個「-」入去算嘞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BTW 如果我整呢個table C欄個名唔會叫「Range」我睇似係叫「Diff since last count」多啲"},{"pid":"1cb369c70abec82d5e68b01b6792abda13b528c2","tid":2140144,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"放去 C2, 向下拉吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=IFERROR(B2-LOOKUP(2,1/(A$1:A1=A2),B$1:B1),&quot;-&quot;)"},{"pid":"0509ea2ae0683dcff081aa6fc0420af3eb8357ca","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f38c8637d35300ab3d12bf38e8d04016f94831","tid":2140144,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8250b26492de92b96845469779a669b78bcaa199","tid":2140144,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":